snippet.title: Lularoe Lawsuit + K's Latest News + Beachbody Goes Public | anti-MLM | Valentine's GRWM
snippet.description:
Hey Beautiful People! February is only 1/2 over and so much has happened!! I also just heard Young Living has a $6 BILLION lawsuit filed against them now too!! Let me know your thoughts in the comments below!
#antimlm #beachbody #lularoe #peloton #meangirls
